Skin care
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We all know the benefits of Green Tea,drink it or apply it,it works both ways.
Loads with lots of antioxidants,anti-inflammatory & antimicrobial properties the green tea face mask is a big hit in the masks category..
.
Here I tried a super easy to make face mask and trust me it really works,just apply the above masks onto your skin and leave it for 20 minutes, it works as a great exfoliator,While exfoliating avoid the area around your eyes and massage your face in circular motion,wash it off and you see the glow for yourself ✨
.
PS: If you want zero wastage,you can also use the used green tea bags 💚
.
Happy Masking
